{"tid":1363401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英泳手拒絕同台頒獎 支那禁藥狗孫楊：你是失敗者 我是贏家","createTime":"2019-07-25T07:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:55:19.000Z","uid":19552,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5353b66af7f41c5ccb8fe40b50806a6f7d4b6ca6","tid":1363401,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"世界游泳錦標賽在南韓光州舉行，中國名將孫楊周二在200米自由泳決賽獲得金牌，但並列銅牌的英國選手史葛響應澳洲名將賀頓的行動，拒絕在頒獎台上與孫楊合照；孫楊其後向史葛稱：「你是失敗者，我是贏家」，結果兩人同遭國際泳聯警告。<br />\n<br />\n孫楊備受禁藥醜聞纏繞，今年1月有消息指他的一個血液樣本被破壞，未能如期送檢，世界運動反禁藥機構告上國際體育仲裁法庭，將於今年9月開審，惟孫楊仍可出戰世錦賽，令不少泳手不滿。"},{"pid":"eef67cae69a977b1e93bf81ed86856cbafeb5b2d","tid":1363401,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:18:26.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"63815fe45e47b4ab07805750e1f2cc95ba95a3c7","tid":1363401,"uid":58630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"唔影相都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c5a9a881e970f344834f6ce3adb1bd9127f811","tid":1363401,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"63815fe45e47b4ab07805750e1f2cc95ba95a3c7","tid":1363401,"uid":58630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"唔影相都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:20:02.000Z","msg":"天朝大國"},{"pid":"e8c924abda05ffe234073192a7a3f7e80afdbc9f","tid":1363401,"uid":213978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:23:14.000Z","msg":"輸左個牌 贏左個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d99511d3cf98c8507b7c4005497e48e3f80149","tid":1363401,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2862671?fbclid=IwAR1Iv1yd5CSXztXm-VHrCSYa5U0TuUTvUB5TZsyZB2ayynadA_eFGHKCOHI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%